	<div class="post-info"><span class="alignleft"><img src="http://www.newslobster.com/wp-content/themes/elegant-brit-b/images/caticon.gif" alt="" /> <a href="http://www.newslobster.com/category/bitcoin" title="View all posts in Bitcoin" rel="category tag">Bitcoin</a>, <a href="http://www.newslobster.com/category/videos" title="View all posts in Videos" rel="category tag">Videos</a> </span><span class="alignright"><img src="http://www.newslobster.com/wp-content/themes/elegant-brit-b/images/comicon.gif" alt="" /> <a href="http://www.newslobster.com/videos/what-is-bitcoin#respond" title="Comment on What Is Bitcoin?">Add Comment (0)</a></span>
